<div class="row column">
  <h4>Input data</h4>
  <pre>
    [
      {
        "key": "South Dakota",
        "value": [
          {
            "key": "2017-10-19T02:36:25-02:00",
            "value": 14
          },
          ...
        ]
      },
      ...
    ]
  </pre>
  <small><code>key</code>, en el array anidado, ha de ser una fecha en formato ISO</small>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row column">
  <h4>Versión simple</h4>
  <code>partial "linechart", metric: "metrica", title: "Lorem", subtitle: "Ipsum"</code>
</div>
<div class="row column mt-s">
  <%= partial "linechart", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::TvShows::GameOfThrones.character, subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row column">
  <h4>Versión con diferentes ratios</h4>
  <div class="callout warning">
    El <code>aspect ratio</code> es un string de la forma <strong>Integer</strong>:<strong>Integer</strong>. Por defecto el valor es <em>4:3</em>
  </div>
  <h4>16:9</h4>
  <code>partial "linechart", ratio: "16:9", metric: "metrica"</code>
</div>
<div class="row column mt-s">
  <%= partial "linechart", ratio: "16:9", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
</div>
<div class="row column">
  <h4>5:4</h4>
  <code>partial "linechart", ratio: "5:4", metric: "metrica"</code>
</div>
<div class="row column mt-s">
  <%= partial "linechart", ratio: "5:4", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row column">
  <h4>Versión sin título ni subtítulo</h4>
  <code>partial "linechart", metric: "metrica"</code>
</div>
<div class="row column mt-s">
  <%= partial "linechart", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s %>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row column">
  <h4>Diferentes colores según su status</h4>
  <div class="callout warning">
    El color por defecto es el de la variable CSS <code>$proposals</code>
  </div>
  <code>partial "linechart", classes: "secondary|warning|success|alert", metric: "metrica"</code>
</div>
<div class="row mt-s">
  <div class="column medium-9">
    <%= partial "linechart", classes: "secondary", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
  </div>
  <div class="column medium-9 pull-right">
    <%= partial "linechart", classes: "warning", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
  </div>
  <div class="column medium-9">
    <%= partial "linechart", classes: "success", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
  </div>
  <div class="column medium-9 pull-right">
    <%= partial "linechart", classes: "alert", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row column">
  <h4>Versión sin tooltip (por defecto <code>tip: true</code>)</h4>
  <code>partial "linechart", metric: "metrica", tip: false</code>
</div>
<div class="row mt-s">
  <div class="column medium-9">
    <%= partial "linechart", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence, tip: false %>
  </div>
  <div class="column medium-9">
    <%= partial "linechart", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence, tip: false %>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row column">
  <h4>Adaptables al contenedor</h4>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <% 2.times do %>
  <div class="column medium-6">
    <%= partial "linechart", metric: "linechart-" + SecureRandom.random_number(2).to_s, title: Faker::Commerce.department(1), subtitle: Faker::Lorem.sentence %>
  </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
